#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.168"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.168:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.168:0.2"
msgid "17. Āghātavagga"
msgstr "17. Resentment"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.168:0.3"
msgid "168. Sīlasutta"
msgstr "168. Ethics"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.168:1.1"
msgid "Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There Venerable Sāriputta addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "an5.168:1.2"
msgid "“dussīlassa, āvuso, sīlavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti sammāsamādhi;"
msgstr ""
"“Reverends, an unethical person, who lacks ethics, has destroyed a vital "
"condition for right immersion."

msgctxt "an5.168:1.3"
msgid ""
"sammāsamādhimhi asati sammāsamādhivipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti "
"yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"When there is no right immersion, one who lacks right immersion has "
"destroyed a vital condition for true knowledge and vision."

msgctxt "an5.168:1.4"
msgid ""
"yathābhūtañāṇadassane asati yathābhūtañāṇadassanavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti "
"nibbidāvirāgo;"
msgstr ""
"When there is no true knowledge and vision, one who lacks true knowledge and "
"vision has destroyed a vital condition for disillusionment and dispassion."

msgctxt "an5.168:1.5"
msgid ""
"nibbidāvirāge asati nibbidāvirāgavipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti "
"vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"When there is no disillusionment and dispassion, one who lacks "
"disillusionment and dispassion has destroyed a vital condition for knowledge "
"and vision of freedom."

msgctxt "an5.168:1.6"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, āvuso, rukkho sākhāpalāsavipanno."
msgstr "Suppose there was a tree that lacked branches and foliage."

msgctxt "an5.168:1.7"
msgid ""
"Tassa papaṭikāpi na pāripūriṃ gacchati, tacopi pheggupi sāropi na pāripūriṃ "
"gacchati."
msgstr "Its shoots, bark, softwood, and heartwood would not grow to fullness."

msgctxt "an5.168:1.8"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, āvuso, dussīlassa sīlavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti sammāsamādhi;"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, an unethical person, who lacks ethics, has destroyed a "
"vital condition for right immersion."

msgctxt "an5.168:1.9"
msgid ""
"sammāsamādhimhi asati sammāsamādhivipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti "
"yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"When there is no right immersion, one who lacks right immersion has "
"destroyed a vital condition for true knowledge and vision."

msgctxt "an5.168:1.10"
msgid ""
"yathābhūtañāṇadassane asati yathābhūtañāṇadassanavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti "
"nibbidāvirāgo;"
msgstr ""
"When there is no true knowledge and vision, one who lacks true knowledge and "
"vision has destroyed a vital condition for disillusionment and dispassion."

msgctxt "an5.168:1.11"
msgid ""
"nibbidāvirāge asati nibbidāvirāgavipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti "
"vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"When there is no disillusionment and dispassion, one who lacks "
"disillusionment and dispassion has destroyed a vital condition for knowledge "
"and vision of freedom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.201"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.168:2.1"
msgid "Sīlavato, āvuso, sīlasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti sammāsamādhi;"
msgstr ""
"An ethical person, who has fulfilled ethics, has fulfilled a vital condition "
"for right immersion."

msgctxt "an5.168:2.2"
msgid ""
"sammāsamādhimhi sati sammāsamādhisampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti "
"yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"When there is right immersion, one who has fulfilled right immersion has "
"fulfilled a vital condition for true knowledge and vision."

msgctxt "an5.168:2.3"
msgid ""
"yathābhūtañāṇadassane sati yathābhūtañāṇadassanasampannassa upanisasampanno "
"hoti nibbidāvirāgo;"
msgstr ""
"When there is true knowledge and vision, one who has fulfilled true "
"knowledge and vision has fulfilled a vital condition for disillusionment and "
"dispassion."

msgctxt "an5.168:2.4"
msgid ""
"nibbidāvirāge sati nibbidāvirāgasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti "
"vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"When there is disillusionment and dispassion, one who has fulfilled "
"disillusionment and dispassion has fulfilled a vital condition for knowledge "
"and vision of freedom."

msgctxt "an5.168:2.5"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, āvuso, rukkho, sākhāpalāsasampanno. Tassa papaṭikāpi pāripūriṃ "
"gacchati, tacopi pheggupi sāropi pāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a tree that was complete with branches and foliage. Its "
"shoots, bark, softwood, and heartwood would grow to fullness."

msgctxt "an5.168:2.6"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, āvuso, sīlavato sīlasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti "
"sammāsamādhi;"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, an ethical person, who has fulfilled ethics, has fulfilled "
"a vital condition for right immersion."

msgctxt "an5.168:2.7"
msgid ""
"sammāsamādhimhi sati sammāsamādhisampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti "
"yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"When there is right immersion, one who has fulfilled right immersion has "
"fulfilled a vital condition for true knowledge and vision."

msgctxt "an5.168:2.8"
msgid ""
"yathābhūtañāṇadassane sati yathābhūtañāṇadassanasampannassa upanisasampanno "
"hoti nibbidāvirāgo;"
msgstr ""
"When there is true knowledge and vision, one who has fulfilled true "
"knowledge and vision has fulfilled a vital condition for disillusionment and "
"dispassion."

msgctxt "an5.168:2.9"
msgid ""
"nibbidāvirāge sati nibbidāvirāgasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti "
"vimuttiñāṇadassanan”ti."
msgstr ""
"When there is disillusionment and dispassion, one who has fulfilled "
"disillusionment and dispassion has fulfilled a vital condition for knowledge "
"and vision of freedom.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.168:2.10"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
